à phản ứng thảm họa.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"89407","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2023-05-30T19:30:07.000Z","cast":["Thái Trác Nghiên","Phương Trung Tín","Đàm Diệu Văn","Lâm Phong","Trương Kế Thông","Ôn Bích Hà","Lily Chung Suk-Wai","Lâm Tuyết","Mashu Ishiwatari","Henry Prince Mak","Angus Yeung Tin-Yue","Trương Nhã Trác","Ricky Chan Po-Yuen","Ngô Đình Diệp","Emotion Cheung Kam-Ching"],"director":["Hà Chú Bồi","Hàn Bình"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Thái Trác Nghiên","name_vi":"Thái Trác Nghiên","name_original":"Charlene Choi Chuek-Yin","tmdb_id":64434,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9f4cT2AgaDsvEwMQRirs0w01mF1.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/64434"},{"name":"Phương Trung Tín","name_vi":"Phương Trung Tín","name_original":"Alex Fong Chung-Sun","tmdb_id":21914,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qQKB910E3e2YLOQs4WdaouJiFJE.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/21914"},{"name":"Đàm Diệu Văn","name_vi":"Đàm Diệu Văn","name_original":"Patrick Tam Yiu-Man","tmdb_id":80374,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aOus8OyhjMqJxnZsI0r5krej8TU.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/80374"},{"name":"Lâm Phong","name_vi":"Lâm Phong","name_original":"Raymond Lam Fung","tmdb_id":89409,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/Ak40P6TWthdQ9diRki5RIcJ6r95.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/89409"},{"name":"Trương Kế Thông","name_vi":"Trương Kế Thông","name_original":"Louis Cheung","tmdb_id":1202564,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ypmPVRkZkjtS7qE3P8nU5GYCXnT.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1202564"},{"name":"Ôn Bích Hà","name_vi":"Ôn Bích Hà","name_original":"Irene Wan","tmdb_id":227780,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rmiDWTjYQMkeBjGNKzJJzMkSeDQ.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/227780"},{"name":"Lily Chung Suk-Wai","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Lily Chung Suk-Wai","tmdb_id":548052,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p